<h1 id="extraction-data">Extraction Data</h1>

<p><img src="/images/pd_1.png" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="by-column">By Column</h2>

<ul>
  <li>DataFrame 에 대괄호는 컬럼 기준으로 인덱싱한다</li>
  <li>대괄호 안에 컬럼명을 넣으면 Series 리턴</li>
  <li>대괄호 안에 다시 대괄호로 리스트를 넘기면 DataFrame 리턴</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-py highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'ticker'</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="nb">type</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">--------------------------</span>
<span class="n">pandas</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">core</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">series</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Series</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/images/pd_17.png" alt="" /></p>

<div class="language-py highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">[[</span><span class="s">'ticker'</span><span class="p">]]</span>

<span class="nb">type</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">----------------------------</span>
<span class="n">pandas</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">core</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">frame</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">DataFrame</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/images/pd_18.png" alt="" /></p>

<div class="language-py highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">filter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">like</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">'(배)'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">head</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/images/pd_19.png" alt="" /></p>

<div class="language-py highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">filter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">regex</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">'\([배원]\)'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">head</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">)</span>
